Refund Policy

At Explore Earth, we strive to provide exceptional service and unforgettable experiences for our alien travelers. However, we understand that circumstances may arise that require you to modify or cancel your reservation. Please review our refund policy outlined below:

    Cancellation and Refund Eligibility:
        Full refunds will be issued for cancellations made at least 72 hours (Earth time) prior to the scheduled start of the tour or activity.
        Cancellations made within 72 hours of the scheduled start time may be subject to a partial refund, at the discretion of [Tourism Company Name].
        No refunds will be issued for cancellations made less than 24 hours before the scheduled start time or for no-shows on the day of the tour or activity.

    Refund Process:
        To request a refund, please contact our customer service team at ExploreEarth@Earth.Earth with your reservation details and reason for cancellation.
        Refunds will be processed back to the original form of payment within 4 business weeks Earth days from the date of cancellation. Please note that it may take additional time for the refunded amount to reflect in your account, depending on your financial institution.

    Tour Changes and Modifications:
        Explore Earth reserves the right to modify or cancel tours or activities due to unforeseen circumstances, including but not limited to weather conditions, natural disasters, or operational constraints.
        In the event of a tour cancellation by Explore earth, travelers will be notified as soon as possible, and a full refund will be provided.

    Exceptions:
        Refund policies may vary for certain special events, custom tours, or package deals. Please refer to the specific terms and conditions outlined at the time of booking for any exceptions.

    Contact Information:
        If you have any questions or concerns regarding our refund policy, please don't hesitate to contact our customer service team at ExploreEarth@Earth.Earth.

By booking a tour or activity with Explore earth, you acknowledge and agree to abide by the terms and conditions of our refund policy as stated above.
